description: One-of-a-kind in Boston! This gorgeous open-concept condo in a South Boston historic treasure features a private entrance & exquisite architectural details including wrought iron work, exposed brick, and classic arched ceilings & passageways. Retreat into your private spa, a blue Canadian slate/river rock oasis leading to a 5-person full-sensory marble steam room. Phenomenal for entertaining, perfect live/work space for an artist, photographer, musician, or anyone who wants a sanctum in the city
